{"tid":1837403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"返大陸探親拜年嘅人唔該唔好再返香港","createTime":"2020-01-23T15:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T16:18:43.000Z","uid":220515,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bd394a3fa557e86ad50ea2a83f21ff4a7b9875f0","tid":1837403,"uid":220515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:24:42.000Z","msg":"你估淨係得報導咗嘅地方爆肺炎咩<br />\n有腦都知實際數字一定唔止咁少<br />\n交通工具 城城省省一定不斷傳染緊<br />\n加上大陸人腦殘又冇防疫知識<br />\n情況會更加嚴峻<br />\n<br />\n咁多位為香港著想嘅巴絲<br />\n如果返咗大陸拜年<br />\n不妨唔好再返香港<br />\n條路自己揀呀 係咁想自殺唔該唔好再返嚟"},{"pid":"7a6dfc8e176f08bb2631872d65fb4762d00753ce","tid":1837403,"uid":220515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:39:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20056978b6379277606e478f52f3d46c8448fa1d","tid":1837403,"uid":220515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:40:47.000Z","msg":"唔好返嚟累人累物<br />\n你覺得自己冇病但有機會潛伏㗎"},{"pid":"f5b29a485353ee4207e096831a6e11db65e4c6a0","tid":1837403,"uid":220515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:45:26.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"16f6ffa561b31a4fed9898bb8f13aed28c9d17ce","tid":1837403,"uid":59297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:46:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hN4EQbF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhN4EQbF.jpg&h=d6d08f34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a4d1d9d3f8e13fbf0bc7407c207df91a5471db8","tid":1837403,"uid":140631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:47:17.000Z","msg":"D人好撚自私 拜小一年會死咩屌"},{"pid":"6f9bd9a70ac0a7487934b7089f2c0827adaecead","tid":1837403,"uid":220515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a4d1d9d3f8e13fbf0bc7407c207df91a5471db8","tid":1837403,"uid":140631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:47:17.000Z","msg":"D人好撚自私 拜小一年會死咩屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:18:43.000Z","msg":"成班都愚孝"}]}